	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-title": "方针与指引",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-body": "请查看维基百科上的可接受和预期内容。",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-mobile-summary": "借鉴最佳实践，打造自由可靠的百科全书。",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-neutral-point-of-view-title": "中立的观点",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-neutral-point-of-view-definition": "内容必须公平、恰当、公正地呈现重要观点。",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-neutral-point-of-view-example-1": "纽约扬基队是历史上最伟大的棒球队。",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-neutral-point-of-view-answer-1-label": "不中立：",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-neutral-point-of-view-answer-1-text": "这种观点缺乏可靠来源的支持。您可以改写成：“纽约扬基队赢过26次世界大赛冠军——几乎是其他任何球队的三倍。”",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-neutral-point-of-view-example-2": "威廉·莎士比亚被广泛认为是英语界最伟大的作家之一。",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-neutral-point-of-view-answer-2-label": "中立：",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-neutral-point-of-view-answer-2-text": "这是恰当的声誉定义。有效性在于许多可靠来源都指出莎士比亚享有此声誉。",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-no-original-research-title": "没有原创研究",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-no-original-research-definition": "条目应通过已发表的来源总结，不应包含用户自己的解释或知识。",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-no-original-research-example-1": "今年11月的气温比去年高。",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-no-original-research-answer-1-label": "包含原创研究：",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-no-original-research-answer-1-text": "该说法没有任何可靠的相关来源资料支持。",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-no-original-research-example-2": "听音乐的人会感到压力减少[可靠来源]。压力减少与寿命延长有关[可靠来源]。因此，听音乐有助于延长寿命。",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-no-original-research-answer-2-label": "包含原创研究：",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-no-original-research-answer-2-text": "不应将来自多个来源的资料整合起来，得出或暗示任何单一来源未明确提出的结论。",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-verifiability-title": "可供查证",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-verifiability-definition": "新增内容应包含引用，提供信息来源。",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-verifiability-example-1": "突发新闻。",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-verifiability-answer-1-label": "原则上不接受：",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-verifiability-answer-1-text": "突发新闻报道往往包含不准确之处。最好在事件发生一两天后，再将详情加入维基百科。这样可以给记者更多时间收集信息，也让调查机构有时间发布官方声明。",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-verifiability-example-2": "来自社交媒体帖子的内容。",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-verifiability-answer-2-label": "不可靠：",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-verifiability-answer-2-text": "来自社交媒体的内容通常不被接受。但如果是由业内知名专家发布，则可以考虑采用。",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-verifiability-example-3": "内容来自可信的学术期刊或书籍。",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-verifiability-answer-3-label": "可靠：",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-verifiability-answer-3-text": "内容应来自于可靠、独立、以事实核查与准确性著称的发表来源。",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-assume-good-faith-title": "假定善意",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-assume-good-faith-definition": "请记住，大多数用户都在努力改进维基百科，而不是故意降低其质量。",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-assume-good-faith-example-1": "“我简直不敢相信你竟然因为编辑格式不正确而搞砸了我的页面，给我停止编辑维基百科！”",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-assume-good-faith-answer-1-label": "非假定善意：",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-assume-good-faith-answer-1-text": "当有编者犯错时，请不要指责他们是恶意行事。",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-assume-good-faith-example-2": "“我注意到您编辑后的格式有点问题。我已经帮您修改好了，另外这个帮助页面可以协助您下一次编辑。”",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-assume-good-faith-answer-2-label": "假定善意：",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-assume-good-faith-answer-2-text": "除非有明显的恶意行为证据，否则应该互相帮助以提高条目质量。",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-examples-button": "范例",
	"personal-dashboard-policies-guidelines-examples-header": "范例：$1"
}
